# Start Page

A customizable start page built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, offering multiple columns and configurable link behaviors. Based upon [Excalith's Start Page](https://github.com/excalith/excalith-start-page).

## Features

- **Multiple Column Layouts**: Supports two and three-column layouts for better organization.
- **Configurable Link Behavior**: Choose whether links open in the same tab or a new tab.
- **Real-Time Search**: Instant highlighting and dimming of links based on your search query.

## Table of Contents

